body:
reason i love 2019 snufkin is because he’s such a dumbass. he literally:

-was lonely after ti-ti-uu was gone and instead of admitting that it was just the feeling of loneliness and maybe he should “know his own mind” first he just says he’s sick

-couldn’t admit he missed moomin and it was only that that helped him find his spring tune

-ate a dirty as fuck carrot

-could see his friends hung out w/ him bc they were scared and says a scary story anyway

-helped children escape from a park without thinking of what would happen to them after that; and

-got his friends arrested for a crime he just decided to do for funsies and bc the timing was perfect

snufkin has one brain cell and he threw it away

summary: Moomin (aka The Sniff Show) episode 2 Reactions
title: Moomin (aka The Sniff Show) episode 2 Reactions
body:
-I like how the theme references that this is a TV show

- BA BABA BA BA BABA BA BA!

- Snufkin stays in his tent like a hobo

- Sniff, the hero of the story, arrives

- Oh shit Moomin is trippin’

- Wait, what is the relative size of these creatures if an ant-lion is that big

-oh an actual lion-thing, not the real ant-lion.

-This got dark really quickly

-Why are they throwing Sniff, the greatest guy ever, into the Sarlacc Pit?

- Sniff’s poor tail, that’s twice in two episodes

- Is Moomin eloping? Where’d he get that ladder?

- Yes, you shouldn’t have thrown the hat into the river

- The hat is bleeding, must have severed one of its arteries

- DON’T TASTE IT DUMBASS!

- BURN IT!

- Raspberry juice is pretty good though

- That was the most passive-aggressive breakfast ever

- Why are the buttons on the back of Snufkin’s coat?

- The Hobgoblin, I knew Norman Osborn was behind this

- Geez Moomin, you can’t just call all Ant-lions stupid, that’s racist.

- In this episode, Snufkin and Moomin commit a murder

- Little My has the attitude and vocal habits of a waitress in a 1950′s diner

- White guy riding a black panther, there’s a metaphor in this somewhere.

- You drowned him, he’s dead, the cops will be after you for sure

- That’s right, laugh Moomin, it’s fun being mean to others

- Back to Snufkin at his hobo camp

- Thread?

- Moominmama must be on some sort of medication. Relatively nonplussed there is a tree growing in her house

- Feed me, Seymour!

- “Try some fruit,” said Eve to Adam

- Oh good, Saruman is here

- “Oh my. Oh goodness me. Oh my. Oh dear.”

- “I don’t suppose you’d have any uncommonly large rubies here, would you?”

- AND SHE ACTUALLY HAS ONE!

- The Hobgoblin is a player in an RPG on a fetch quest that got bugged out and the Moomins are just hapless NPCs

- “He’s not bad for a Hobgolbin.” More racism, Moomin?

- It’s going to take them days to clear out their house now.

- Exit whimsy.
